{
  "stem": "24470.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That coat served me as a cover on my bunk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Um, we slept in our clothes because there was no change of clothes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Um, next to me was-- uh, were two sisters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of them was a lunatic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Uh, when the moon was out-- I remember vividly-- she got up from her bunk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She walked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She recited history in Polish-- Polish history, like a professor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she walked, and sometimes she walked out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Sometimes she walked back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she slept right next to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it was another experience that I remember.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In the morning, early, a German came to take us out of the, uh, barrack.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were counted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were led to work-- to machines where we worked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "At the big, large hall where the machines were being, uh, worked on were three-- three Germans-- uh, two German women, very vicious, very mean.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They supervised the work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh, no, they were the Germans, the German women, not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Uh, there was a Jewish kapo also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't recall anything wrong or drastic per-- personally to us, uh, that I knew of.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the German women were vicious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was an office within that hall with a glass top, uh, all around the office.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the bottom was covered, not-- not, uh, see-through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a German officer supervising everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we called him 'the American,' because he happened to be-- uh, he showed himself to be a human being.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Uh, when he called someone to his office under the pretext that he's going to punish or scream-- shouted and screamed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But under the cover, he gave them sandwiches.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we had a-- sort of a-- uh, we-- we called him, in secret, 'the American.' Uh, but the women were very mean.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
